sentences: He joined the group in 2007 as the accordionist.
In 2008, Chumbawamba released an album called  The Boy Bands Have Won.
In the autumn of 2009 he toured northern England in their self-penned pantomime, a comedy musical entitled Riot, Rebellion & Bloody Insurrection with the Red Ladder Theater Company.
